    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean about infrasound but it doesn't explain the rhythm. i timed it. it follows this weird 4-second cycle of increasing intensity then a sudden drop. it's too precise for just a transformer or something. it's like it's pulsing on a carrier wave or something. u think it's possible for that kind of signal to be modulated to carry information or influence?",
